          "subject": "=New Project Initiated: {{$json.title}}",
          "emailFormat": "both",
          "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333;\">\n  <p>\n    Dear {{$json.first_name || 'User'}} {{$json.last_name || ''}},\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    We are pleased to inform you that a new project, \n    <strong>{{$json.title}}</strong>, has been successfully initiated and you have been assigned as Project Manager.\n  </p>\n\n  <h3 style=\"color: #2c3e50;\">Project Overview</h3>\n\n  <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; max-width: 600px;\">\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Project Name</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.title}}</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.description}}</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Priority</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.priority}}</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Start Date</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.start_date}}</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Planned End Date</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.end_date}}</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Current Status</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.status}}</td>\n    </tr>\n<tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Project Link</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://web.gophygital.work/vas/projects/details/{{$json.id}}\" target=\"_blank\">\n      View Project Details\n    </a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">\n    Please review the project details, validate timelines, and initiate the necessary planning and execution activities.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Regards,<br/>\n    <strong>Project Management Office</strong>\n  </p>\n</div>",
          "options": {}
